WEBVTT

00:06:54.440 --> 00:07:00.520
so that Arabic teaching and learning
becomes fun, easy and accessible globally.

00:07:01.520 --> 00:07:05.720
With this book, I hope to save
my nation's beautiful script.

00:07:06.480 --> 00:07:10.936
(Applause)

00:07:10.960 --> 00:07:12.160
Thank you.

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:20.016
Working on this project
was a form of visual meditation,

00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:21.296
like a Sufi dance,

00:07:21.320 --> 00:07:23.160
a prayer to a better planet.

00:07:23.920 --> 00:07:27.536
One set of building blocks
made two languages.

00:07:27.560 --> 00:07:29.160
LEGO is just a metaphor.

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:33.216
It's because we are all made
of the same building unit,